data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Horseshoe Bay Resort! This 3 BD, 2 1/2 BA residence offers resort-style living at its finest, complete with a rare assumable VA loan at 2.25%.  Prime location on the prestigious Slickrock golf course with easy access to resort amenities including four golf courses, spa, marina, and exclusive restaurants. Plus, you're just an hour away from Austin.  Step inside to discover the allure of hardwood floors throughout the kitchen, living room, and baths, creating an ambiance of warmth and sophistication. The master bath showcases Tarantino tile, double vanities, and a walk-in shower, ensuring a spa-like experience every day.  The heart of the home lies in the gourmet kitchen, complete with granite countertops and ample space for culinary creations while enjoying guests in the spacious living area.  Relax by the wood-burning fireplace in the living area or entertain guests on the great covered patio, surrounded by a wrought iron fence and outdoor lighting, perfect for enjoying Texas evenings. The exterior features timeless stone accents and a tile roof for both durability and style. This home has great curb appeal with landscaped stone beds and large shade trees and is located on a serene cul-de-sac.  For the avid golfer, the two-car garage includes dedicated golf storage, ensuring easy access to equipment for impromptu rounds on the course.   Don't miss this opportunity to live luxuriously in Horseshoe Bay Resort with a low-interest assumable loan. Schedule a showing today!
